{"tid":817723,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實海龜條飲管係點樣入去鼻哥？","createTime":"2018-09-13T14:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T01:38:06.000Z","uid":12449,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"49c2573c516cac39d9ccf537ea22e06e3e461d6b","tid":817723,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"會唔會係人為塞入，然後sell新產品？<br />\n<br />\n塑膠係胃係口就好易明，因為佢地會誤食膠袋之類。<br />\n<br />\n但係條飲管塞到咁入，就真係好難理解，個鼻咁細個洞。<br />\n<br />\n平時啲海龜成堆膠袋、condom、水樽蓋仲死撚埋都冇咁大回響。<br />\n<br />\n反而飲管佔整體海洋垃圾不足1%嘅就咁大反應。<br />\n<br />\n成件事係唔合理喎！"},{"pid":"bcfeec62084342c3dfa98d8618313646e978a3d2","tid":817723,"uid":58257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"唔通隻龜take野又影埋比你睇咩。"},{"pid":"2cfd44460a712b319e8398e5b614293d0995eb0c","tid":817723,"uid":104658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"隻龜諗住用條飲管撩鼻屎  點知塞得太入"},{"pid":"5dccfaf5d7c57c199c69eeac4991b8a245ef5891","tid":817723,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"食緊飲管嗰陣打乞嚏咪走左去個鼻度<br />\n<br />\n利申 : CE bio拎B"},{"pid":"2f52b3d54fd994ebd5142405b317d13e1aff41c8","tid":817723,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cfd44460a712b319e8398e5b614293d0995eb0c","tid":817723,"uid":104658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"隻龜諗住用條飲管撩鼻屎  點知塞得太入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"老人探肛咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6618568953afbce8e300ed3c6aebbb63c3643944","tid":817723,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dccfaf5d7c57c199c69eeac4991b8a245ef5891","tid":817723,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"食緊飲管嗰陣打乞嚏咪走左去個鼻度<br />\n<br />\n利申 : CE bio拎B"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"好似食麵噴麵咁？"},{"pid":"